# Project Root Commands

**All Flutter commands must be run from [visionspark/](mdc:visionspark)** (contains pubspec.yaml)

Running from any other directory will fail with "No pubspec.yaml file found."

Example:
```bash
cd visionspark
flutter build apk --split-per-abi
```

